    dc:description "Figure 26. Map of known geographic distribution of Agrostis species, based on herbarium specimen data A A. perennans B A. scabra C A. stolonifera D A. subpatens E A. subrepens F A. tolucensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/891261" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

